    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and verified rear subframe integrity. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with factory precision. Equipped with the variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery out of corners, this driver-focused machine offers a visceral mechanical connection often lost in modern counterparts.",
      "price": 34500.0,
