      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home. This car has been so reliable for me and is still in really solid shape! It drives like a dream and has been well-loved over the years. Perfect if you need something dependable and ready to hit the road today. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
