      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. The chassis features reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension bushings have been refreshed to maintain precise toe and camber alignment, while the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for effective heat dissipation. A mechanically honest example optimized for performance.",
